{"tid":1987732,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"羅志祥韓國開唱燃爆全場，對漂亮女主持的這一舉動暴露個人修養。","createTime":"2020-04-24T16:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T22:44:25.000Z","uid":231132,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"84ceb77ffbbc450c6b11c57fd4131fb3b28289d5","tid":1987732,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:17:47.000Z","msg":"2018年Asia Song Festival在韓國釜山唱響了，吸引了韓國眾多當紅愛豆參與，如Red Velvet、SEVENTEEN、momoland、Wanna One、MXM、Bewhy等，本次音樂節的主持人是SJ隊長利特和 女團momoland的門面Nancy。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20181004/2869845aad034987810e70b3b74fa900.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fq_70%2Cc_zoom%2Cw_640%2Fimages%2F20181004%2F2869845aad034987810e70b3b74fa900.jpeg&h=8ef6a602&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 作為一個亞洲音樂節，當然少不了其他亞洲國家的歌手了。 據悉，菲律賓的代表是女歌手Morissette Amon，而中國唯一受邀藝人是羅志祥與旗下男團CTO。 本次，羅志祥帶來了歌曲《夠了》+《鬧翻天》，CTO男團則表演《C.T.O》➕《Insomnia》，羅志祥和CTO的精彩開唱可謂是嗨翻全場，帥炸了！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20181004/9395157629dd45a6b1e9a04753d94f0c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fq_70%2Cc_zoom%2Cw_640%2Fimages%2F20181004%2F9395157629dd45a6b1e9a04753d94f0c.jpeg&h=57f49d55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 在表演空隙中，羅志祥透露了他最想合作的韓國藝人是SJ的利特，還和對方一起跳SJ火遍全世界的名曲《Sorry, Sorry》，引發了無數人的回憶。 其實，SJ此前前往台灣做宣傳的時候，經常上羅志祥主持的節目，兩人早已是舊識，如今再度同框，讓人感慨萬千。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20181004/0abb8e94881f4e2d9bf5f6aebc6c141a.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fq_70%2Cc_zoom%2Cw_640%2Fimages%2F20181004%2F0abb8e94881f4e2d9bf5f6aebc6c141a.webp&h=91176bfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 羅志祥在和利特共舞時，旁邊還站著一位漂亮女主持，她就是女團momoland的門面Nancy。 為了不讓Nancy覺得尷尬，羅志祥示意她一起跳舞，想給她更多的鏡頭，這一貼心舉動暴露了羅志祥的個人修養。 看來羅志祥不僅很會照顧女生，他的臨場反應更是一流的，怪不得羅志祥有那麼多的綜藝邀約。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20181004/04a1edd3ba60455fad6466733b4de258.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fq_70%2Cc_zoom%2Cw_640%2Fimages%2F20181004%2F04a1edd3ba60455fad6466733b4de258.webp&h=6f33bb0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 羅志祥在本次亞洲音樂節上，不管是舞台表現方面，還是個人修養方面，都給觀眾們留下了相當深刻的印象。 最後，小韓也希望羅志祥以後能夠經常出現在舞台上，給大家帶來更多好音樂。"},{"pid":"d3f00b4ec73265c1b2a251fa9ef3d0ad9004f811","tid":1987732,"uid":210112,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:30:08.000Z","msg":"妍雨啊"},{"pid":"afb69a039923b5c880c1759db975898f3d5b175b","tid":1987732,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:30:58.000Z","msg":"我都想屌NANCY阿..."},{"pid":"ce7b685733ef41572655d7a890f52cbc610ede9e","tid":1987732,"uid":555,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K1hOER4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK1hOER4.gif&h=a65cc26a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ejB83En.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FejB83En.gif&h=9cef2660&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91d0721fff4682eb43481e481244037ab3f3836","tid":1987732,"uid":13013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a01027606a487db3ee0a38bace17c061e0c382","tid":1987732,"uid":76115,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:44:31.000Z","msg":"問題唔係有冇屌過, 而係有冇屌埋屎眼"},{"pid":"800d44288f2e5d903d8046868b331d92aa87499b","tid":1987732,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:44:42.000Z","msg":"無事發生"},{"pid":"e9bf8807f6f42b2fa643dd26da80235286705